77. **conversion-jobs** ‚Äî Applies to: `arch.diagram.agent.svc` ‚Äî Example: `ray-test-dev-0001-a1b2c3-conversion-jobs-017868795096`.
78. **notifications-email** ‚Äî Applies to: `notification.svc` SNS ‚Äî Example: `ray-test-dev-0001-a1b2c3-notifications-email`.
79. **shared-lustre** ‚Äî Applies to: FSx purpose ‚Äî Example: `ray-test-shared-lustre`.

### Anti-patterns (forbidden)

80. **Double hyphen** ‚Äî Applies to: all ‚Äî `--` anywhere in a physical name or `DEP_KEY` segment.
81. **Hard-coded project** ‚Äî Applies to: all ‚Äî literal `ray-test` or `ray_test` in module defaults instead of `var.solution` / constants link.
82. **Type in HCL label** ‚Äî Applies to: Terraform ‚Äî `aws_s3_bucket_logs` style resource names.
83. **Tags in this file** ‚Äî Applies to: all ‚Äî define tags only in **`resource-taging.mdc`**.

